en-US.title: UCI Health Pediatric Gender Diversity Program
en-US.description: The UCI Health Pediatric Gender Diversity Program provides tailored, comprehensive health care, and support services to transgender individuals and their families. The clinic offers a wide range of medical, mental-health and social services that cater specifically to the needs of the transgender community, affirming their identity and promoting their health and well-being.

address: 101 The City Dr S, Orange, CA 92868, USA
